title: Blue Jays beat Rangers 6-3 to win wild Game 5
text:
> Texas Blue Jays beat Rangers 6-3 to win wild Game 5 Texas Rangers' Elvis Andrus slams his bat into the ground after striking out to end the inning against the Toronto Blue Jays during the eighth inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Division Series, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015 in Toronto. (Frank Gunn/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
